column1: PM2.5: percentage of population and exceedances. Results are shown at country level  (including EU28 and EEA33 aggregates).
tot_pop_exc: sum of total population assigned to each stations for stations having above_TV?=1
nb_of_station_exc: count of stations having above_TV?=1
tot_pop_no_exc: sum of total population assigned to each stations for stations having above_TV?=0
nb_of_station_no_exc: count of stations having above_TV?=0

Note: one station (station_european_code) can be counted several times if the same station shows several concentration statistics for the same year (distinct measurements recorded under different measurement_european_group_code)
